<plot>Sophie, thrown out of home by her deadbeat husband Steve because she looks too much like Doris Day, seeks shelter in a display home overnight and likes it so much she decides to stay. But soon she is discovered by hapless sales agent Gary. At first he wants to throw her out but then realizes her potential as a human exhibit. All is going swimmingly until love rears its ugly head.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?096415</url></doc>
